msgstr ""

#: ../../../../getting-started/mix-otp/supervisor-and-application.markdown:424
msgid "At the end of the day, tools like Observer is one of the main reasons you want to always start processes inside supervision trees, even if they are temporary, to ensure they are always reachable and introspectable."
